rows.label: tlk43310142_03_msg0001
rows.name:
It's a shame we didn't get to
wipe out those damn Superbians.

rows.label: tlk43310142_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Our armor is made from the hardened
excretions of the Invidian Divine
Beast, referred to as "coral".

rows.label: tlk43310142_03_msg0003
rows.name:
It's strong enough to withstand
even a blast from Superbia's
most powerful weapon, Tortoga.

rows.label: tlk43310142_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I would have relished the chance to prove
once and for all that our soldiers are
categorically superior to theirs.
